Invocation Name: daybreak yoga
des: Do you find it difficult to get out of bed in the morning? This skill can help! This skill will give you some yoga poses to do while you are still in bed. It talks you through a routine designed to ease you out of your bed and into your day. It will keep providing yoga poses until you are ready to get out of bed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
